                                        "body": "<span class=\"code_addition\">The provisions of <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/district-of-columbia/ibc-2015/chapter/1/scope-and-administration#1\">Chapter 1</a> of the <i>Building Code</i>, Title 12-A DCMR shall establish the general administrative requirements applicable to <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/district-of-columbia/irc-2015/chapter/2/definitions#mechanical_system_\">mechanical systems</a> and inspection requirements of the <i>Residential Code</i>.</span>  The administrative provisions of  Chapter&nbsp;<span class=\"code_addition\">1 of the <i>Building Code</i>, Title 12-A DCMR,</span> shall also apply to the mechanical requirements of Chapters <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/district-of-columbia/irc-2015/chapter/13/general-mechanical-system-requirements#13\">13</a> through <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/district-of-columbia/irc-2015/chapter/24/fuel-gas#24\">24</a>.",
