                                        "body": "Except as otherwise provided for in this code, a provision in this code shall not require the removal, <i><a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/district-of-columbia/irc-2015/chapter/2/definitions#alteration_\">alteration</a></i> or abandonment of, nor prevent the continued use and maintenance of, an existing <a class=\"autolink\" href=\"/viewer/district-of-columbia/irc-2015/chapter/2/definitions#mechanical_system_\">mechanical system</a> lawfully in existence at the time of the adoption of this code.",
